{"tid":282674,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[急問]尚華書院 北京普通話進修課程 有無用","createTime":"2017-06-13T14:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T14:46:14.000Z","uid":92878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d408ac5e799d1715b52547acd3ab45cdb1e9ec84","tid":282674,"uid":92878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"我自己普通話真係好差  想係暑假增值下自己<br />\n我係 香港專上學生協進會 見到 尚華書院 北京普通話進修課程<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hktsg.net/pth.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktsg.net%2Fpth.php&d=J9oVfvWgaPX5x2D7PFKzrgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=df2ef61a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hktsg.net/pth.php</a><br />\n佢有個 學成保證(若同學於公開考試不合格，可免費重讀應試技巧課程部份 *出席率需達80%或以上) <br />\n而且 持續進修基金資助 (CEF) 會資助八成學費  好似幾好咁<br />\n咁岩見到大家都話尚華係黑店 唔知有無過來人可以分享下<br />\nps我今日打上去問完佢已經叫我上去比錢..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2843cb8901159fda82a2e3d00cd716ed86624ac8","tid":282674,"uid":115751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"頂，我都報左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到咁多人鬧間野，而家好驚阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04f80cfe6b7b0ebe2fe735da05230ca91253fdf","tid":282674,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝好運"},{"pid":"fc73aef7e0ba23f6957a50c4b7c879363d06a11b","tid":282674,"uid":92878,"li